36,"file_path":"/eLGBjQIfNUTeicUjrv2jgn5WMZf.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.784,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/aLbdTIwWEzftPXyOsdH7DInYFE8.jpg","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/wB2Lc2geApxhtXk1UgPI4hyCiQM.jpg","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1360,"height":765,"file_path":"/yIeF4sR80v2aMgLmeB7d55VaVeM.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1680,"height":945,"file_path":"/mCpAOflVsAGQiE7MYy9RgU1VZPE.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/mXDx6HJaCtlMZdtH4kDbb7Eu19S.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0}]},"enriched_at":"2026-02-26T03:30:39.379+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"Solo Dio perdona","runtime":90,"tagline":"","homepage":"http://www.wildside.fr/cinema/only-god-forgives-473.html","overview":"Julian allena pugili di thai boxe a Bangkok perchè ha ucciso il padre e non gli è rimasto altro se non fuggire dall'America dove la madre è a capo di un'organizzazione mafiosa. Suo fratello l'ha seguito ma non si è adattato alla vita locale e l'ennesima prostituta massacrata è il suo biglietto per l'obitorio. La cosa non è tollerabile e il capofamiglia si trasferisce a Bangkok intenzionata a fare giustizia a modo suo. Le regole di Bangkok non sono però quelle americane e la catena di vendette si interrompe subito quando tocca ad un poliziotto in pensione abile maneggiatore di spade che risponde al sangue con più sangue. In un mondo in cui tutti sono mobilitati per vendetta il più inadeguato però appare essere proprio Julian."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":89,"tagline":"Time to meet the Devil.","homepage":"","overview":"Julian, who runs a Thai boxing club as a front organization for his family's drug smuggling operation, is forced by his mother Crystal to find and kill the individual responsible for his brother's recent death."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"Tylko Bóg wybacza","runtime":90,"tagline":"Czas na spotkanie z diabłem.","homepage":"","overview":"Julian (Ryan Gosling) w Bangkoku jest właścicielem klubu, w którym prowadzi nie do końca legalne interesy. Kiedy jego brat Billy (Tom Burke) zostaje zamordowany, życie Juliana radykalnie się zmienia. Ich matka (Kristin Scott Thomas) oczekuje, że młodszy syn odnajdzie zabójców brata i go pomści. Mężczyzna – mimo oporów i wątpliwości – postanawia dotrzeć do człowieka, który prawdopodobnie stoi za śmiercią Billy'ego. Wie tylko, że w ciemnych zaułkach miasta nazywają go Aniołem Zemsty...  [opis dystrybutora dvd]"},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"Csak Isten bocsáthat meg","runtime":90,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Julian az igazságszolgáltatás elől menekülő bűnöző, aki egy boksziskolát működtet Bangkokban, ezzel leplezve drogügyleteit. Amikor testvérét a helyi maffia meggyilkolja, az egy bűnszervezet keresztanyjaként tisztelt édesanyja bosszúra szólítja fel. A férfi kezdetben hezitál, mivel testvére is egy bosszú áldozata lett - megerőszakolt és meggyilkolt egy prostituáltat -, ám enged az anyai akaratnak és véres bosszúhadjáratba kezd. A harcművészetben is jártas Julian-nek szembe kell néznie egy titokzatos ex-zsaruval, és a korrupt és kegyetlen bangkoki alvilággal."},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":90,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"À Bangkok, Julian, qui a fui la justice américaine, dirige un club de boxe thaïlandaise servant de couverture à son trafic de drogue. Sa mère, chef d’une vaste organisation criminelle, débarque des Etats-Unis afin de rapatrier le corps de son fils préféré, Billy : le frère de Julian vient en effet de se faire tuer pour avoir sauvagement massacré une jeune prostiuée. Ivre de rage et de vengeance, elle exige de Julian la tête des meurtriers. Julian devra alors affronter Chang, un étrange policier à la retraite, adulé par les autres flics..."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Só Deus Perdoa","runtime":90,"tagline":"Hora de conhecer o Diabo.","homepage":"","overview":"Um homem (Ryan Gosling) vive um exílio em Bagkok durante dez anos, depois de ter matado um policial. Ele mantém um clube de boxe, que funciona como disfarce para o tráfico de drogas. Quando seu irmão é assassinado depois de matar uma prostituta, o protagonista recebe a visita de sua mãe, que pretende resgatar o cadáver do filho mais novo e vingar-se dos homens que o mataram."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":90,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Die ungleichen Brüder Julian und Billy leben in Bangkoks Rotlichtviertel inmitten von Luxus, Sex, Sünde und Verbrechen. Dreh- und Angelpunkt für ihre illegalen Geschäfte ist ihr Kickbox-Club. Der unbarmherzige Kopf des Familienkartells ist jedoch ihre unnahbare, schöne und erbarmungslose Mutter Crystal. Als Billy eine Frau tötet, sorgt ein selbsternannter Racheengel auf seine ganz eigene Art für Gerechtigkeit und Billy bezahlt seine Tat mit dem Leben. Die trauernde Crystal sinnt auf Rache und schickt Julian auf eine blutige Jagd nach Vergeltung durch Bangkoks Unterwelt ..."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"รับคำท้าจากพระเจ้า","runtime":0,"tagline":"ถึงเวลาเจอยมบาล","homepage":"","overview":"Only God Forgives เป็นเรื่องราวเกี่ยวกับ มาเฟีย ที่หลบหนีคดีความผิด และมากบดานอยู่ที่ไทย โดยเปิด ค่ายมวย เพื่อบังหน้ากับน้องชายของตัว และคิดว่าจะออกจากวงการนี้ไปอย่างเงียบๆ แต่แล้วก็ดูเหมือนว่าเรื่องมันจะไม่ง่ายอย่างที่คิด เมื่อน้องชายของเขา ดันไปฆ่า โสเภณีไทย จนเสียชีวิต ทำให้กรมตำรวจไทยต้องส่งตำรวจที่ขึ้นชื่อว่าฝีมือดีที่สุดมาตามล่าตัวของเขาทั้ง 2 คน จนกระทั่งท้ายสุดเรื่องราวต้องไปเกิดขึ้นบนเวทีมวยแสนชุลมุน เรื่องราวจะเป็นต่อไปอย่างไรรอติดตามได้เร็วๆนี้"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":90,"tagline":"","homepage":"http://www.wildside.fr/cinema/only-god-forgives-473.html","overview":"Julian, een Amerikaan die in Bangkok woont, is een gerespecteerde figuur in de onderwereld. Samen met zijn broer Billy baat hij een Thai boxing club uit die in feite een dekmantel is voor drugssmokkel naar Amerika. Wanneer Billy vermoord wordt, komt hun moeder Crystal uit Amerika over om het lichaam te repatriëren. Crystal zelf is het hoofd van een machtige criminele organisatie en is gewend te krijgen wat ze wil. In dit geval: de dood van haar zoon wreken."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"Только Бог простит","runtime":89,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Джулиан, бежавший от американского правосудия, руководит в Бангкоке клубом тайского бокса, который служит ему прикрытием для торговли наркотиками. Его мать, глава крупной преступной организации, приезжает из США, чтобы забрать тело своего любимого сына Билли: брата Джулиана только что убили за зверскую расправу над молодой проституткой. Охваченная яростью и жаждой мести мать требует, чтобы Джулиан нашел и покарал убийц. Молодому человеку придется столкнуться с Чангом — странным полицейским на пенсии, которого обожают его коллеги."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"Sadece Tanrı Affeder","runtime":90,"tagline":"Şeytanla tanışmanın vakti geldi","homepage":"","overview":"Bir cinayet işlediği için Bangkok'a kaçan Julian on senedir burada sürgünde yaşamaktadır. Yeraltı dünyası tarafından saygı gösterilen bir suçlu olan Julian kardeşiyle birlikte uyuşturucu ticareti yapmak için paravan olarak kullandıkları bir boks kulübünün işletmeciliğini yapar. Bir gün Julian'ın kardeşi bir kadını öldürmesinin ardından belalı kişilerce vahşice öldürülür. Bunun üzerine sert mizaçlı bir patroniçe olan anneleri Jenna ilk uçakla oraya gelerek Julian'dan kardeşinin katillerini bulup intikamını almasını ve cehennemi ayağa kaldırmasını isteyecektir. Ancak karşılarında şeytanın ta kendisi vardır."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"唯神能恕","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"十年前，Julian（瑞恩·高斯林 Ryan Gosling 饰）因杀了一名警察而跑路到了曼谷，现在他经营着一家泰拳俱乐部以掩饰毒品走私交易。Julian的弟弟Billy（Tom Burke 饰）因残杀了一名妓女而遭到“复仇天使”退休警察Chang（Vithaya Pansringram 饰）的杀害。身为庞大犯罪组织头目的Julian的母亲Crystal (克里斯汀·斯科特·托马斯Kristin Scott Thomas饰演）来到曼谷为爱儿收尸。满腔愤怒与强烈报复心态的母亲要求Julian为兄弟报仇，使得Julian不得不与Chang正面交锋......"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Jen Bůh odpouští","runtime":90,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Před deseti lety Julian zabil policajta, ale podařilo se mu utéct. Dnes je z něj jeden z největších drogových dealerů v Bangkoku. Když Julianův bratr zabije prostitutku, policie si pozve na pomoc Changa – Anděla pomsty, který dovolí otci zavražděné, aby ho osobně zabil. Tím však rozpoutá peklo, protože do situace se vloží Julianova matka, šéfka jedné z nejmocnějších kriminálních organizací, která Juliana vysílá pomstít svého bratra."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":90,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Julian pyörittää Bangkokissa thainyrkkeilyklubia, jonka kulisseissa käydään huumekauppaa. Kun Julianin veli murhaa alaikäisen prostituoidun ja saa maksaa teosta hengellään, rikollisorganisaatiota johtava Julianin äiti saapuu kaupunkiin vaatimaan kostoa."},"name":"suomi","iso_639_1":"fi","iso_3166_1":"FI","english_name":"Finnish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":90,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Gangstern Julian driver en thaiboxningsklubb som fungerar som täckmantel för familjens narkotikaimperium. Då hans bror Billy mördas kommer deras mor Crystal till Bangkok för att ta med sig liket från sin förste son hem och för att få Julian till att hämnas sin brors mord."},"name":"svenska","iso_639_1":"sv","iso_3166_1":"SE","english_name":"Swedish"},{"data":{"title":"Sólo Dios perdona","runtime":89,"tagline":"Llego la hora de conocer al Diablo","homepage":"http://www.onlygodforgives.com/","overview":"En Bangkok, Julian, un fugitivo de la justicia estadounidense, dirige un club de boxeo tailandés que actúa como tapadera para su tráfico de estupefacientes. Su madre, jefe de una amplia organización criminal, desembarca procedente de Estados Unidos para repatriar el cuerpo de su hijo favorito, Billy: el hermano de Julian ha sido asesinado tras haber masacrado salvajemente a una joven prostituta. Llena de odio y venganza, exige a Julian la cabeza de los asesinos. Julian deberán entonces enfrentarse a Chang, un extraño policía jubilado, adulado por los demás policías."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":90,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Amerikanske Julien sælger narko gennem sin bokseklub i Bangkoks underverden. Da hans bror, Billy, slår en prostitueret ihjel, tillader politimanden Chang, at pigens far dræber Billy for at få hævn. Juliens frygtindgydende mor ankommer for at hente sin førstefødtes lig, og hun beder Julien om at hævne broren. Men han er oppe imod Chang, som konsekvent udøver karmisk retfærdighed med sit samuraisværd."},"name":"Dansk","iso_639_1":"da","iso_3166_1":"DK","english_name":"Danish"},{"data":{"title":"Μόνο Ο Θεός Συγχωρεί","runtime":90,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.facebook.com/onlygodforgivesfilm","overview":"Ο Αμερικανός Τζούλιαν διευθύνει έναν πυγμαχικό όμιλο στην Ταϊλάνδη, ο οποίος είναι βιτρίνα της οικογενειακής επιχείρησης διανομής ναρκωτικών. Όταν ο αδελφός του, Μπίλι, δολοφονείται, η μητέρα του Τζούλιαν, η Τζίνα, καταφτάνει στην πόλη. Το μόνο που αποζητά είναι εκδίκηση και θέτει υπεύθυνο τον Τζούλιαν για να την πάρει. Οι σύνδεσμοι του Τζούλιαν με τον υπόκοσμο τον οδηγούν στον «Άγγελο Εκδίκησης», έναν συνταξιοδοτημένο αστυνόμο που γνωρίζει τα πάντα και είναι ταυτόχρονα δικαστής και τιμωρός. Η Τζίνα θέλει από τον Τζούλιαν να τον σκοτώσει, χωρίς να σκεφτεί οποιοδήποτε κόστος."},"name":"ελληνικά","iso_639_1":"el","iso_3166_1":"GR","english_name":"Greek"},{"data":{"title":"רק אלוהים סולח","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"ג'וליאן ובילי הם שני אחים אמריקאים המתגוררים בתאילנד ומנהלים מכון אגרוף מצליח בלב ליבה של בנגקוק. המכון הוא רק סיפור כיסוי לעסקים המפוקפקים שהשניים מנהלים: סמים, הלבנת הון ועוד. הסיפור לוקח תפנית לרעה כאשר בילי גורם למותה של יצאנית מקומית ומשלם על כך בחייו. כאשר אימם, קריסטל מגיעה לתאילנד כדי לזהות את גופת בנה היא נפגשת עם ג'וליאן ומפצירה בו למצוא את האנשים שהרגו את אחיו ולנקום. ג'וליאן נקרע בין בקשת אמו לבין הרצון שלו להשאיר את השקט כפי שהוא. אך כאשר הוא מגלה מי באמת הרג את אחיו הוא לא רואה דרך חזרה ויוצא למסע הרג רווי אלימות ברחבי העיר."},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"オンリー・ゴッド","runtime":90,"tagline":"その復讐は 神への挑戦","homepage":"","overview":"ビリーとジュリアン兄弟は故郷アメリカから逃げ、タイのバンコクでボクシングジムを経営しながら、その裏でドラッグビジネスに手を染めていた。ある日、兄ビリーが若い娼婦をなぶり殺しにした末、彼女の父親に殺害される。犯罪組織を仕切る兄弟の母親がアメリカから急行し……。"},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"Doar Dumnezeu iartă","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Acțiunea are loc în Bangkok. Cu 10 ani în urmă, Julian (Ryan Gosling) a ucis un polițist și a fugit. Acum conduce un club de box thailandez care reprezintă un paravan pentru afacerile lui ilegale de trafic de droguri. Este respectat de lumea criminală însă înăuntrul său se simte gol și singur. Când fratele lui Julian ucide o prostituată, poliția îl convoacă pe polițistul pensionat supranumit \"Îngerul Răzbunării\" (Vithaya Pansringarm). Chang îi permite tatălui victimei să-l ucidă pe asasinul acesteia. Mama lui Julian, Crystal (Kristin Scott Thomas) este capul unei organizații criminale. Acesta ajunge în Bangkok pentru a îngropa cadavrul fiului său. Femeia îl trimite pe Julian să-l găsească pe criminalul fratelui său și să dezlănțuie iadul. Obsedat de \"Îngerul Răzbunării\", Julian îl provoacă la un meci de box thailandez sperând ca atunci când îl ucide să găsească o eliberarea sufletească, însă Chang câștigă. Furioasă, Jenna plănuiește acum o răzbunare sângeroasă."},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"Só Deus Perdoa","runtime":90,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Um homem (Ryan Gosling) vive um exílio em Bagkok durante dez anos, depois de ter matado um policial. Ele mantém um clube de boxe, que funciona como disfarce para o tráfico de drogas. Quando seu irmão é assassinado depois de matar uma prostituta, o protagonista recebe a visita de sua mãe, que pretende resgatar o cadáver do filho mais novo e vingar-se dos homens que o mataram."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"온리 갓 포기브스","runtime":0,"tagline":"더욱 차가워진 복수! 오직 신 만이 용서한다!","homepage":"","overview":"환락과 폭력으로 물든 도시 방콕에서 복싱장을 운영하는 ‘줄리안’(라이언 고슬링)은 마약밀매를 하던 형 ‘빌리’가 잔인하게 살해당하자 범인을 찾아 나선다. 아들의 장례식을 위해 방콕으로 온 ‘크리스탈’(크리스틴 스콧 토마스)은 ‘줄리안’에게 형을 죽인 사람을 찾아 당장 죽일 것을 지시한다. ‘빌리’의 죽음의 이유를 찾던 ‘줄리안’은 형의 죽음의 배후에 ‘악마’라 불리는 전직 경찰 ‘챙’이 연루되어 있음을 알게 되는데…"},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"Само Бог прощава","runtime":90,"tagline":"Време е да срещнете дявола","homepage":"","overview":"Джулиан живее в изгнание в Банкок, където управлява тайландски боксьорски клуб, служещ като прикритие за операцията по пренасяне на наркотици, ръководена от семейството му. Когато убиват брат му Били, майка им Джена пристига в града. Тя е жадна за мъст и принуждава Джулиан да намери убиеца. Връзките му с престъпния подземен свят го водят направо до Ангела на отмъщението, вездесъщ пенсиониран полицай, който е едновременно съдия и прокурор. Джена иска Джулиан да го убие, което ще му струва скъпо."},"name":"български език","iso_639_1":"bg","iso_3166_1":"BG","english_name":"Bulgarian"},{"data":{"title":"Само бог прашта","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Џулијан води боксерски клуб у Бангкоку, као параван за породични посао кријумчарења дроге. Када је Џулијанов брат Били убијен, њхова мајка Џена долази у град. Она жели освету и тера Џулијана да пронађе убицу. Џулијанови контакти га одводе директно до “Анђела освете”, пензионисаног полицајца који зна све и влада поџемљем. Џена захтева да Џулијан убије “Анђела освете”, што ће га скупо коштати."},"name":"Srpski","iso_639_1":"sr","iso_3166_1":"RS","english_name":"Serbian"},{"data":{"title":"Only God Forgives","runtime":90,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Julian, som driver en Thai-boksing klubb som en skalkeskjul for sin families narkotikasmugling, blir tvunget av sin mor Jenna til å finne og drepe personen som er ansvarlig for hans brors nylige død."},"name":"Norsk","iso_639_1":"no","iso_3166_1":"NO","english_name":"Norwegian"},{"data":{"title":"Atleidžia tik dievas","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Amerikietis Džulianas (Ryanas Goslingas) slapstosi nuo teisėsaugos egzotiškame Bankoke. Jaunuolis, prisidengdamas tailandietiško kikbokso klubo direktoriaus pareigomis, turi narkotikų verslą. Bet jo ramų gyvenimą sudrumsčia žiauriai nužudžiusio nepilnametę brolio Bilio mirtis. Vos išgirdusi apie šeimos tragediją į Tailandą atskrenda jų despotiška motina Džena (Kristin Scott Thomas). Ji pati vadovauja pavojingai ir įtakingai nusikaltėlių organizacijai. Moteris liepia Džulianui surasti ir nubausti Bilio žudikus. Jaunuolis išsiaiškina, kad su brolio nužudymu susijęs bebaimis Bankoko policininkas Čangas, pakrikštytas Keršto angelu"},"name":"Lietuvių","iso_639_1":"lt","iso_3166_1":"LT","english_name":"Lithuanian"},{"data":{"title":"Seul Dieu pardonne","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"CA","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Лише Бог прощає","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Головний герой фільму, Джуліан, займається торгівлею наркотиків, процвітаючи у злочинному світі Банґкоку. Але пріоритети змінюються, коли мати змушує його знайти і розправитися з вбивцями його брата. На цьому шляху він зустрінеться з дуже дивним поліцейським."},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"},{"data":{"title":"Solo Dios Perdona","runtime":90,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"En Bangkok, el joven Julian, un fugitivo de la justicia estadounidense, dirige un club de boxeo tailandés que actúa como tapadera para tráfico de drogas. Su madre, jefa de una poderosa organización criminal, desembarca procedente de Estados Unidos para repatriar el cuerpo de su hijo favorito, Billy: el hermano de Julian ha sido asesinado tras haber violado y matado salvajemente a una joven prostituta. Llena de odio y deseo de venganza, su madre exige a Julian la cabeza de los asesinos, por lo que éste deberá enfrentarse a Chang, un extraño policía jubilado, muy respetado y querido por sus ex-compañeros."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"فقط خدا میبخشه","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"«جولین» یک قاچاقچی مواد مخدر در بانگکوک است. وضعیت زندگی او زمانی پیچیده می شود که مادرش از او می خواهد که قاتل برادرش را هرطور شده پیدا کند و او را به سزای عملش برساند..."},"name":"فارسی","iso_639_1":"fa","iso_3166_1":"IR","english_name":"Persian"},{"data":{"title":"Piedos tikai Dievs","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Latviešu","iso_639_1":"lv","iso_3166_1":"LV","english_name":"Latvian"},{"data":{"title":"Samo bog odpušča","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Slovenščina","iso_639_1":"sl","iso_3166_1":"SI","english_name":"Slovenian"},{"data":{"title":"Len Boh odpúšťa","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Pred desiatimi rokmi Julian zabil policajta, ale podarilo sa mu ujsť. Dnes je jedným z najväčších drogových dílerov v Bangkoku. Keď Julianov brat zabije prostitútku, polícia požiada o pomoc Čanga, Anjela pomsty, ktorý umožní otcovi zavraždenej ženy, aby ho zabil sám. To však vyvolá peklo, pretože Juliánova matka, šéfka jednej z najmocnejších zločineckých organizácií, zasiahne a pošle Juliána, aby pomstil jej brata."},"name":"Slovenčina","iso_639_1":"sk","iso_3166_1":"SK","english_name":"Slovak"},{"data":{"title":"罪無可赦","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"罪無可赦","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"朱利安與哥哥比利從美國流亡到泰國，一個大雨滂沱的夜裡比利姦殺了一名少女，更慘死在憤怒的少女父親手下。他們的母親悲痛收屍，並要朱利安為哥哥報仇。想不到深入調查後朱利安發現讓比利客死異鄉的元凶其實另有其人，因仇恨漸趨瘋狂的母親讓朱利安不得不違背本意讓雙手染血，這場血腥復仇將如何收場？"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"}],"reviews_tmdb":[{"id":"5b3878b60e0a2675e000153e","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/5b3878b60e0a2675e000153e","author":"Per Gunnar Jonsson","content":"$11","created_at":"2018-07-01T06:46:14.557Z","updated_at":"2024-05-16T15:21:17.065Z","author_details":{"name":"Per Gunnar Jonsson","rating":5,"username":"Dark Jedi","avatar_path":null}},{"id":"5f3ff9e6028f14003455d56b","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/5f3ff9e6028f14003455d56b","author":"RustyBoi","content":"A challenging piece of cinema. Definitely not for everyone. The cinematography is breathtaking, and the violence is stomach turning. 8/10","created_at":"2020-08-21T16:44:22.616Z","updated_at":"2021-06-23T15:58:42.951Z","author_details":{"name":"","rating":8,"username":"RustyBoi","avatar_path":null}},{"id":"621e823f3acd20006b9e331f","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/621e823f3acd20006b9e331f","author":"r96sk","content":"It has all the ingredients that I'd usually love in a film, but the pacing lets it down for me.\r\n\r\n<em>'Only God Forgives'</em> is pretty dark and strikingly gory, with the stylish cinematography really shining through to set the right tone. Ryan Gosling, meanwhile, is good in a role which is similar to his one in 2011's <em>'<a href=\"https://letterboxd.com/film/drive-2011/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Drive</a>'</em>, which was also directed by Nicolas Winding Refn. Kristin Scott Thomas is solid, though I couldn't get away from the thought that her character was made to be portrayed by Toni Collette. Vithaya Pansringarm plays it cool as his character.\r\n\r\nAll in all, I enjoyed it. I just didn't love it. It's a little too stop/start for my liking, as in it felt like I was watching a series of events as opposed to a fully fleshed out plot; I don't mean that the scenes feel unconnected, it just feels like every scene is too much its own thing in terms of storytelling.","created_at":"2022-03-01T20:29:51.557Z","updated_at":"2022-03-01T20:29:51.557Z","author_details":{"name":"","rating":7,"username":"r96sk","avatar_path":"/mwR7rFHoDcobAx1i61I3skzMW3U.jpg"}}],"recommendations":[{"id":18533,"adult":false,"title":"Bronson","video":false,"overview":"A young man who was sentenced to 7 years in prison for robbing a post office ends up spending 30 years in solitary confinement. During this time, his own personality is supplanted by his alter ego, Charles Bronson.","genre_ids":[18,28,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.0904,"vote_count":2619,"poster_path":"/6diyyGIbBNiANsdIaCGtyv4IofR.jpg","release_date":"2009-03-13","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/uc8FwdCQi3eD7JIbyiZuzo5n6Jv.jpg","original_title":"Bronson","original_language":"en"},{"id":301365,"adult":false,"title":"The Neon Demon","video":false,"overview":"When aspiring model Jesse moves to Los Angeles, her youth and vitality are devoured by a group of beauty-obsessed women who will take any means necessary to get what she has.","genre_ids":[27,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.6155,"vote_count":3884,"poster_path":"/3rBo2AfWSlvsPmYFdJsNUMfkNIo.jpg","release_date":"2016-05-31","vote_average":6.51,"backdrop_path":"/xcfjWEmSpgJe8htlg1qFTwQfPG7.jpg","original_title":"The Neon Demon","original_language":"en"},{"id":97367,"adult":false,"title":"The Place Beyond the Pines","video":false,"overview":"A motorcycle stunt rider considers committing a crime in order to provide for his wife and child, an act that puts him on a collision course with a cop-turned-politician.","genre_ids":[18,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.2521,"vote_count":5102,"poster_path":"/vY5j2xQzMGWmxBuhQo0HfA4Lxqb.jpg","release_date":"2013-03-20","vote_average":6.985,"backdrop_path":"/qCsaZ2GoaCn5vmOUD9kCsyabr9o.jpg","original_title":"The Place Beyond the Pines","original_language":"en"},{"id":37861,"adult":false,"title":"Valhalla Rising","video":false,"overview":"Scandinavia, 1,000 AD. For years, One Eye, a mute warrior of supernatural strength, has been held prisoner by the Norse chieftain Barde. Aided by Are, a boy slave, One Eye slays his captor and together he and Are escape, beginning a journey into the heart of darkness. On their flight, One Eye and Are board a Viking vessel, but the ship is soon engulfed by an endless fog that clears only as the crew sights an unknown land. As the new world reveals its secrets and the Vikings confront their terrible and bloody fate, One Eye discovers his true self.","genre_ids":[12,18,28,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.498,"vote_count":1298,"poster_path":"/7LBMcAx6XHwEduIsBYipvUke9n.jpg","release_date":"2009-09-04","vote_average":6.108,"backdrop_path":"/5UTOmyAIe7icGgjc5ETOZNMITmj.jpg","original_title":"Valhalla Rising","original_language":"en"},{"id":2061,"adult":false,"title":"Pusher","video":false,"overview":"A drug pusher grows increasingly desperate after a botched deal leaves him with a large debt to a ruthless drug lord.","genre_ids":[28,80,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.6152,"vote_count":834,"poster_path":"/9Myfvq4e2BySE5aosX8UzV9cUME.jpg","release_date":"1996-08-30","vote_average":6.995,"backdrop_path":"/fO8xmjkGsDBzyGdw6ZgwqVoK50w.jpg","original_title":"Pusher","original_language":"da"},{"id":64690,"adult":false,"title":"Drive","video":false,"overview":"Driver is a skilled Hollywood stuntman who moonlights as a getaway driver for criminals. Though he projects an icy exterior, lately he's been warming up to a pretty neighbor named Irene and her young son, Benicio. When Irene's husband gets out of jail, he enlists Driver's help in a million-dollar heist. The job goes horribly wrong, and Driver must risk his life to protect Irene and Benicio from the vengeful masterminds behind the robbery.","genre_ids":[18,53,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":7.4073,"vote_count":13380,"poster_path":"/602vevIURmpDfzbnv5Ubi6wIkQm.jpg","release_date":"2011-09-15","vote_average":7.582,"backdrop_path":"/iymDDg4upZWgpbSeiE1JCjsSPBs.jpg","original_title":"Drive","original_language":"en"},{"id":10316,"adult":false,"title":"The Ides of March","video":false,"overview":"Dirty tricks stand to soil an ambitious young press spokesman's idealism in a cutthroat presidential campaign where 'victory' is relative.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.0898,"vote_count":2657,"poster_path":"/w8t4UnJnC24S9ygoaFgmMzRbErd.jpg","release_date":"2011-10-07","vote_average":6.676,"backdrop_path":"/lO3QqiOh2AO47oUVJcgr7axxftH.jpg","original_title":"The Ides of March","original_language":"en"},{"id":282296,"adult":false,"title":"My Old Lady","video":false,"overview":"Mathias Gold is a down-on-his-luck New Yorker who inherits a Parisian apartment from his estranged father. But when he arrives in France to sell the vast domicile, he's shocked to discover a live-in tenant who is not prepared to budge. His apartment is a viager—an ancient French real estate system with complex rules pertaining to its resale—and the feisty Englishwoman Mathilde Girard, who has lived in the apartment with her daughter Chloé for many years, can by contract collect monthly payments from Mathias until her death.","genre_ids":[10749,35,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3916,"vote_count":282,"poster_path":"/hPLAUrmJkXdv1sEtIqk9EwXvmbH.jpg","release_date":"2014-09-09","vote_average":6.216,"backdrop_path":"/coQ2NtQbLEmrIVE2CnzCr5j3hYK.jpg","original_title":"My Old Lady","original_language":"en"},{"id":159622,"adult":false,"title":"Terms and Conditions May Apply","video":false,"overview":"Have you ever read the Terms and Conditions and Privacy Policies connected to every website you visit, phone call you make, or app you use? Of course you haven’t. But those agreements allow corporations to do things with your personal information you could never even imagine. This film explores the intent hidden within these ridiculous agreements, and reveals what corporations and governments are legally taking from you and the outrageous consequences that result from clicking “I accept.”","genre_ids":[99],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3221,"vote_count":198,"poster_path":"/hiXXUS7LVqALDNugz5kRvS0Xkx1.jpg","release_date":"2013-07-12","vote_average":6.942,"backdrop_path":"/9sfGWVz2D2EvfDzqhP22xwJh7tT.jpg","original_title":"Terms and Conditions May Apply","original_language":"en"},{"id":118624,"adult":false,"title":"Doomsday Book","video":false,"overview":"In 'A Brave New World', a virus brings the city to ruins and zombies flood the streets of Seoul. In 'The Heavenly Creature', a robot reaches enlightenment while working at a temple, but its creators deem this phenomenon a threat to mankind. In the final segment, 'Happy Birthday', a young girl logs onto a strange website and places an order for a new billiard ball for her father. Soon afterwards a meteor heads toward Earth and people flee to underground bomb shelters.","genre_ids":[878,14,18,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.2796,"vote_count":112,"poster_path":"/1HQBqpGtsN8f65kzHoZhLKbMchr.jpg","release_date":"2012-04-11","vote_average":6.147,"backdrop_path":"/2VbPypoIBkomTTs7tBsp4uMaxrp.jpg","original_title":"인류멸망보고서","original_language":"ko"},{"id":77334,"adult":false,"title":"The Terrace","video":false,"overview":"Eight Italian politicians from the communist party gather on a terrace in Rome for a get-together. They discuss about their past, present and future.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4283,"vote_count":155,"poster_path":"/9VQpe6Olw355r0PmxmgBBs5BFSk.jpg","release_date":"1980-02-08","vote_average":7.181,"backdrop_path":"/rjEoEfJDhDlYW0bMdeIntKFuSkS.jpg","original_title":"La terrazza","original_language":"it"},{"id":14275,"adult":false,"title":"Hoop Dreams","video":false,"overview":"Every school day, African-American teenagers William Gates and Arthur Agee travel 90 minutes each way from inner-city Chicago to St. Joseph High School in Westchester, Illinois, a predominately white suburban school well-known for the excellence of its basketball program. Gates and Agee dream of NBA stardom, and with the support of their close-knit families, they battle the social and physical obstacles that stand in their way. This acclaimed documentary was shot over the course of five years.","genre_ids":[99],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7382,"vote_count":326,"poster_path":"/gLzHl2XBtVwycl8DxdOXRHPm8G3.jpg","release_date":"1994-09-12","vote_average":7.577,"backdrop_path":"/pYeiEm55NySzK9ksKlQGlFQNapz.jpg","original_title":"Hoop Dreams","original_language":"en"},{"id":42557,"adult":false,"title":"The SuperVips","video":false,"overview":"A satire of modern society or perhaps just a funny tale for children, depending on your age, mood or liking. Recounting the adventures of the last in a line of Supermen, the film pokes fun at the processes that lie behind advertising, politics and our consumer society.","genre_ids":[16,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3017,"vote_count":41,"poster_path":"/tMFN0FJ6toIgFM2V7uIaumiNOOD.jpg","release_date":"1968-10-31","vote_average":7.427,"backdrop_path":"/gTlV7iUWg2inFhISHIVLUSPD8MW.jpg","original_title":"Vip, mio fratello superuomo","original_language":"it"},{"id":172631,"adult":false,"title":"Family Weekend","video":false,"overview":"A 16-year-old girl takes her parents hostage after they miss her big jump-roping competition.","genre_ids":[35,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.4398,"vote_count":223,"poster_path":"/RiUNV96HPP14OfB7ILEOe2Vj26.jpg","release_date":"2013-03-28","vote_average":6.291,"backdrop_path":"/mMjRFMOuFxsL2elALlm5v8CA7ud.jpg","original_title":"Family Weekend","original_language":"en"},{"id":355065,"adult":false,"title":"The People vs. Fritz Bauer","video":false,"overview":"It is the late 1950s. Flourishing under the economic miracle, Germany grows increasingly apathetic about confronting the horrors of its recent past. Nevertheless, Fritz Bauer doggedly devotes his energies to bringing the Third Reich to justice. One day Bauer receives a letter from Argentina, written by a man who is certain that his daughter is dating the son of Adolph Eichmann. Excited by the promising lead, and mistrustful of a corrupt judiciary system where Nazis still lurk, Bauer journeys to Jerusalem to seek alliance with Mossad, the Israeli secret service. To do so is treason — yet committing treason is the only way Bauer can serve his country.","genre_ids":[36,18,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4642,"vote_count":212,"poster_path":"/jufmPUcwJYCRJe2q3pgAP0IavhC.jpg","release_date":"2015-09-13","vote_average":6.8,"backdrop_path":"/eG69D0ftcKmYeCKCIkzLbKihTva.jpg","original_title":"Der Staat gegen Fritz Bauer","original_language":"de"},{"id":12628,"adult":false,"title":"Playing God","video":false,"overview":"Stripped of his medical license after performing an operation while high on amphetamines, famed LA surgeon Dr Eugene Sands abandons his former life only to find himself crossing paths with Raymond Blossom, an infamous counterfeiter. Employed as a \"gun-shot doctor\" when Raymond's associates cannot risk visiting a hospital, Eugene is lured deep into the criminal world and becomes entangled with his boss's girlfriend.","genre_ids":[18,28,53,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7458,"vote_count":121,"poster_path":"/faYRZjtBMNygM7spt72yrs72hC8.jpg","release_date":"1997-10-17","vote_average":5.483,"backdrop_path":"/gHqEy16wIeGEfoCdROYaTpCcPUb.jpg","original_title":"Playing God","original_language":"en"},{"id":113148,"adult":false,"title":"Prince Avalanche","video":false,"overview":"Two highway road workers spend the summer of 1988 away from their city lives. The isolated landscape becomes a place of misadventure as the men find themselves at odds with each other and the women they left behind.","genre_ids":[35,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5813,"vote_count":331,"poster_path":"/kCfs93bW6FdLIZoYN5pYILysyx4.jpg","release_date":"2013-02-13","vote_average":6.136,"backdrop_path":"/5vNn4LReE0p5AFDVpspYU2ZY8HV.jpg","original_title":"Prince Avalanche","original_language":"en"},{"id":330544,"adult":false,"title":"Bessie","video":false,"overview":"The story of legendary blues performer, Bessie Smith, who rose to fame during the 1920s and '30s.","genre_ids":[18,10402,10770],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7797,"vote_count":125,"poster_path":"/kanAZsL3kZwFWRuR6tqLvNrEFco.jpg","release_date":"2015-05-16","vote_average":6.336,"backdrop_path":"/8pPoIJJ7ylLULMbpHNWdg8Ab7CF.jpg","original_title":"Bessie","original_language":"en"},{"id":241765,"adult":false,"title":"The Outsider","video":false,"overview":"Revolves around a British military contractor Lex Walker who is told his daughter has died. When he arrives in Los Angeles and discovers the body is not hers, he begins an investigation.","genre_ids":[28,80,18,9648,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5989,"vote_count":69,"poster_path":"/iYRFAxQpB0VVVO17cPC8nEyZiLN.jpg","release_date":"2015-06-21","vote_average":4.5,"backdrop_path":"/nxWUUSYOTEAjARGUI9EcTBSMo2u.jpg","original_title":"The Outsider","original_language":"en"},{"id":104524,"adult":false,"title":"Helter Skelter","video":false,"overview":"Top model Lilico, having recently undergone multiple cosmetic surgeries, begins to experience troubling side effects. As she desperately tries to retain her perfect image, Lilico descends into a world of nightmares and makes those around her miserable.","genre_ids":[18,27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.988,"vote_count":165,"poster_path":"/nrTHLNNjejHgoVVkJUowkTpndI0.jpg","release_date":"2012-07-14","vote_average":6.673,"backdrop_path":"/oe5zpoVher2uZSvkhrHKi9H7TtW.jpg","original_title":"ヘルタースケルター","original_language":"ja"}],"similar_content":[{"id":77,"adult":false,"title":"Memento","video":false,"overview":"Leonard Shelby is tracking down the man who raped and murdered his wife. The difficulty of locating his wife's killer, however, is compounded by the fact that he suffers from a rare, untreatable form of short-term memory loss. Although he can recall details of life before his accident, Leonard cannot remember what happened fifteen minutes ago, where he's going, or why.","genre_ids":[9648,53],"popularity":9.0867,"vote_count":15928,"poster_path":"/fKTPH2WvH8nHTXeBYBVhawtRqtR.jpg","release_date":"2000-10-11","vote_average":8.176,"backdrop_path":"/7Wev9JMo6R5XAfz2KDvXb7oPMmy.jpg","original_title":"Memento","original_language":"en"},{"id":78,"adult":false,"title":"Blade Runner","video":false,"overview":"In the smog-choked dystopian Los Angeles of 2019, blade runner Rick Deckard is called out of retirement to terminate a quartet of replicants who have escaped to Earth seeking their creator for a way to extend their short life spans.","genre_ids":[878,18,53],"popularity":12.05,"vote_count":14715,"poster_path":"/63N9uy8nd9j7Eog2axPQ8lbr3Wj.jpg","release_date":"1982-06-25","vote_average":7.94,"backdrop_path":"/hJ5R9d6QuH3tzr8L8neZZTuzNXm.jpg","original_title":"Blade Runner","original_language":"en"},{"id":141,"adult":false,"title":"Donnie Darko","video":false,"overview":"After narrowly escaping a bizarre accident, a troubled teenager is plagued by visions of a large bunny rabbit that manipulates him to commit a series of crimes.","genre_ids":[14,18,9648],"popularity":9.0293,"vote_count":13208,"poster_path":"/fhQoQfejY1hUcwyuLgpBrYs6uFt.jpg","release_date":"2001-01-19","vote_average":7.762,"backdrop_path":"/msCHK5Kh1YbdZ0zPJ2nzPUhhSN9.jpg","original_title":"Donnie Darko","original_language":"en"},{"id":101,"adult":false,"title":"Léon: The Professional","video":false,"overview":"Léon, the top hit man in New York, has earned a rep as an effective \"cleaner\". But when his next-door neighbors are wiped out by a loose-cannon DEA agent, he becomes the unwilling custodian of 12-year-old Mathilda. Before long, Mathilda's thoughts turn to revenge, and she considers following in Léon's footsteps.","genre_ids":[80,18,28],"popularity":13.1027,"vote_count":15811,"poster_path":"/bxB2q91nKYp8JNzqE7t7TWBVupB.jpg","release_date":"1994-09-14","vote_average":8.294,"backdrop_path":"/jRJrQ72VLyEnVsvwfep8Xjlvu8c.jpg","original_title":"Léon","original_language":"fr"},{"id":103,"adult":false,"title":"Taxi Driver","video":false,"overview":"Suffering from insomnia, disturbed loner Travis Bickle takes a job as a New York City cabbie, haunting the streets nightly, growing increasingly detached from reality as he dreams of cleaning up the filthy city.","genre_ids":[80,18],"popularity":13.4122,"vote_count":13213,"poster_path":"/ekstpH614fwDX8DUln1a2Opz0N8.jpg","release_date":"1976-02-09","vote_average":8.127,"backdrop_path":"/9uddYYTNcLWpzUkl5iw1RUYhLhY.jpg","original_title":"Taxi Driver","original_language":"en"},{"id":115,"adult":false,"title":"The Big Lebowski","video":false,"overview":"Jeffrey 'The Dude' Lebowski, a Los Angeles slacker who only wants to bowl and drink White Russians, is mistaken for another Jeffrey Lebowski, a wheelchair-bound millionaire, and finds himself dragged into a strange series of events involving nihilists, adult film producers, ferrets, errant toes, and large sums of money.","genre_ids":[35,80],"popularity":8.0204,"vote_count":11962,"poster_path":"/9mprbw31MGdd66LR0AQKoDMoFRv.jpg","release_date":"1998-03-06","vote_average":7.839,"backdrop_path":"/hXsy4XCCHrUk81XoRhcooyWejao.jpg","original_title":"The Big Lebowski","original_language":"en"},{"id":274,"adult":false,"title":"The Silence of the Lambs","video":false,"overview":"Clarice Starling is a top student at the FBI's training academy.  Jack Crawford wants Clarice to interview Dr. Hannibal Lecter, a brilliant psychiatrist who is also a violent psychopath, serving life behind bars for various acts of murder and cannibalism.  Crawford believes that Lecter may have insight into a case and that Starling, as an attractive young woman, may be just the bait to draw him out.","genre_ids":[80,53,18],"popularity":3.7028,"vote_count":17611,"poster_path":"/uS9m8OBk1A8eM9I042bx8XXpqAq.jpg","release_date":"1991-02-14","vote_average":8.346,"backdrop_path":"/aYcnDyLMnpKce1FOYUpZrXtgUye.jpg","original_title":"The Silence of the Lambs","original_language":"en"},{"id":275,"adult":false,"title":"Fargo","video":false,"overview":"Jerry, a small-town Minnesota car salesman is bursting at the seams with debt... but he's got a plan. He's going to hire two thugs to kidnap his wife in a scheme to collect a hefty ransom from his wealthy father-in-law. It's going to be a snap and nobody's going to get hurt... until people start dying. Enter Police Chief Marge, a coffee-drinking, parka-wearing - and extremely pregnant - investigator who'll stop at nothing to get her man. And if you think her small-time investigative skills will give the crooks a run for their ransom... you betcha!","genre_ids":[80,18,53],"popularity":8.1869,"vote_count":8901,"poster_path":"/rt7cpEr1uP6RTZykBFhBTcRaKvG.jpg","release_date":"1996-03-08","vote_average":7.847,"backdrop_path":"/747dgDfL5d8esobk7h4odaOFhUq.jpg","original_title":"Fargo","original_language":"en"},{"id":290,"adult":false,"title":"Barton Fink","video":false,"overview":"A renowned New York playwright is enticed to California to write for the movies and discovers the hellish truth of Hollywood.","genre_ids":[35,18,53],"popularity":3.1782,"vote_count":1839,"poster_path":"/oDkp5iClJ9WKJGtKHz8BydodHC3.jpg","release_date":"1991-08-01","vote_average":7.458,"backdrop_path":"/3VTY3ZaP5UDLgfI1z2HJHEgesnA.jpg","original_title":"Barton Fink","original_language":"en"},{"id":184,"adult":false,"title":"Jackie Brown","video":false,"overview":"Jackie Brown is a flight attendant who gets caught in the middle of smuggling cash into the country for her gunrunner boss. When the cops try to use Jackie to get to her boss, she hatches a plan — with help from a bail bondsman — to keep the money for herself.","genre_ids":[80,18,53],"popularity":5.6686,"vote_count":6820,"poster_path":"/rOUx7qg4KmEh1juEDwqzbDSL1Nr.jpg","release_date":"1997-12-25","vote_average":7.359,"backdrop_path":"/gvaeY5kz3wHrMU6xLdnybziwYXw.jpg","original_title":"Jackie Brown","original_language":"en"},{"id":187,"adult":false,"title":"Sin City","video":false,"overview":"Welcome to Sin City. This town beckons to the tough, the corrupt, the brokenhearted. Some call it dark… Hard-boiled. Then there are those who call it home — Crooked cops, sexy dames, desperate vigilantes. Some are seeking revenge, others lust after redemption, and then there are those hoping for a little of both. A universe of unlikely and reluctant heroes still trying to do the right thing in a city that refuses to care.","genre_ids":[80,53],"popularity":6.3534,"vote_count":8680,"poster_path":"/i66G50wATMmPrvpP95f0XP6ZdVS.jpg","release_date":"2005-04-01","vote_aver